OL,7,FRecent changes to population
OL,8,Fmanagement laws are damaging local
OL,9,Fbusinesses, according to the
OL,10,FConfederation of Guernsey Industry
OL,11,F(CGI).
OL,13,FIn April, the States updated the law
OL,14,Fso it would be easier for businesses
OL,15,Fto hire staff from all over the world.
OL,17,FUnder the plans, medium-term permits
OL,18,Fwere scrapped and short-term ones
OL,19,Fcould only be renewed for up to three
OL,20,Fyears.
